---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mt-20 px-6 font-sans">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 relative">
        <div
            class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-20 h-20 bg-pink-500/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"
        >
        </div>
        <div
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center p-3 mb-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-100 to-purple-100 dark:from-pink-900/30 dark:to-purple-900/30 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-pink-200 dark:border-pink-800"
        >
            <Icon name="mdi:beaker-outline" class="w-10 h-10 text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400" />
        </div>
        <h2
            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold pb-2 bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-600 via-purple-600 to-indigo-600 drop-shadow-sm"
        >
            Alquimia Digital: <br class="hidden md:block" />Transmuta Píxeles en Arte Tangible
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
            Bienvenido al <strong>Estudio Definitivo de Patrones</strong>. Un motor de <em
                class="text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 font-bold not-italic"
                >inteligencia cromática</em
            > diseñado para arquitectos del Pixel Art, maestros del Miyuki y visionarios del punto de
            cruz. Tu puente entre lo digital y lo artesanal.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-20">
        <div
            class="bg-white/50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-3xl border border-white/20 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 group"
        >
            <div
                class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
            >
                <Icon name="mdi:grid" class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-4">
                La Retícula Inteligente
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                Nuestro algoritmo de <strong>submuestreo espacial</strong> no solo "encoge" tu imagen.
                Analiza la estructura visual para mapear grupos de píxeles complejos a celdas individuales,
                preservando la integridad de siluetas y bordes como un dibujante experto.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div
            class="bg-white/50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-3xl border border-white/20 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 group"
        >
            <div
                class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900/30 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
            >
                <Icon name="mdi:palette" class="w-7 h-7 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-4">
                Cuantización K-Means
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                Implementamos una variante del algoritmo <strong>K-Means Clustering</strong> que encuentra
                matemáticamente los tonos "centroides" de tu imagen. Fidelidad visual asombrosa con una
                paleta minimalista de 12, 24 o 32 tonos.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span
            class="text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400 font-bold tracking-wider text-sm uppercase bg-pink-50 dark:bg-pink-900/20 px-4 py-1 rounded-full"
            >Workflow</span
        >
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mt-4">Maestría en 3 Pasos</h3>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6 mb-24">
        <div
            class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-50 to-white dark:from-gray-800 dark:to-gray-900 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden"
        >
            <div
                class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-yellow-400/10 rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/3"
            >
            </div>
            <div
                class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-yellow-100 dark:bg-yellow-900/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-black text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400 shadow-inner"
            >
                1
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-2">
                    La Selección Perfecta
                </h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                    Busca <strong>alto contraste</strong>, iluminación dramática y formas icónicas.
                    Los retratos con fondo limpio, logotipos y arte vectorial se traducen
                    maravillosamente.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div
            class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-50 to-white dark:from-gray-800 dark:to-gray-900 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden"
        >
            <div
                class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-indigo-400/10 rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/3"
            >
            </div>
            <div
                class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-black text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 shadow-inner"
            >
                2
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-2">
                    Calibración Dimensional
                </h4>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-3">
                    <div
                        class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-3 rounded-lg text-sm border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700"
                    >
                        <strong class="block text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 mb-1"
                            >Miyuki Delica</strong
                        >
                        50 cuentas ≈ 8cm
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-3 rounded-lg text-sm border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700"
                    >
                        <strong class="block text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 mb-1"
                            >Hama Midi</strong
                        >
                        50 cuentas ≈ 25cm
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-3 rounded-lg text-sm border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700"
                    >
                        <strong class="block text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 mb-1"
                            >Punto de Cruz</strong
                        >
                        1 celda = 1 puntada
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div
            class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-50 to-white dark:from-gray-800 dark:to-gray-900 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden"
        >
            <div
                class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-green-400/10 rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/3"
            >
            </div>
            <div
                class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-black text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 shadow-inner"
            >
                3
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-2">
                    Ejecución Zen (Modo Visión de Túnel)
                </h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                    Nuestro sistema <strong>Visión de Túnel</strong> actúa como tu asistente personal,
                    oscureciendo el ruido visual y resaltando quirúrgicamente solo la fila activa. Concentración
                    absoluta.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-10">
        Lienzos Infinitos
    </h3>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-20">
        <div
            class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300"
        >
            <Icon name="mdi:needle" class="w-10 h-10 text-pink-500 mb-4" />
            <h5 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-gray-800 dark:text-white">Joyería Textil</h5>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                Patrones intrincados para telares y brazaletes geométricos.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div
            class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300"
        >
            <Icon name="mdi:grid" class="w-10 h-10 text-purple-500 mb-4" />
            <h5 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-gray-800 dark:text-white">Cross-Stitch</h5>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                Esquemas modernos listos para ser bordados pixel a pixel.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div
            class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300"
        >
            <Icon name="mdi:border-all" class="w-10 h-10 text-indigo-500 mb-4" />
            <h5 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-gray-800 dark:text-white">Mosaicos</h5>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                Murales de gran escala usando teselas cerámicas simplificadas.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div
            class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300"
        >
            <Icon name="mdi:controller-classic" class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-500 mb-4" />
            <h5 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-gray-800 dark:text-white">Retro Gaming</h5>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                Assets y sprites con estética 8-bit auténtica en segundos.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div
        class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-black rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 text-center text-white shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden mb-12"
    >
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-white/[0.05] bg-[size:20px_20px]"></div>
        <div
            class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-pink-500/20 rounded-full blur-[100px] -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="relative z-10">
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">El Renacimiento Artesanal</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-6">
                En una era de pantallas efímeras, crear algo físico es un acto revolucionario. Esta
                herramienta no busca automatizar el arte, sino <strong>empoderar al artesano</strong
                >. Te damos la precisión computacional para que tus manos puedan construir legados
                duraderos.
            </p>
            <p class="font-mono text-pink-400 text-sm tracking-widest uppercase">
                // Sube tu imagen · Define tu visión · Crea
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
